title: Donald Trump seeks a sharp a contrast with Ben Carson’s Seventh-day Adventist faith
text: JACKSONVILLE, Fla. -- Donald Trump on Saturday contrasted his Presbyterian faith with that of Seventh-day Adventists, apparently attempting to draw attention to and raise doubts about Republican presidential rival Ben Carson's religious beliefs. Speaking at a campaign rally here, Trump was in the midst of discussing his standing in the polls, including recent Iowa surveys […] ...
